text: Iskush () is a rural locality (a selo) in Mayadykovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 8 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Dyurtyuli, 4 from Mayadyk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Iskush
